PLACEHOLDER — not a real keystore. Generate one with:
  keytool -genkeypair -v \
    -keystore debug-learnlauncher.keystore \
    -alias learnlauncher \
    -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000 \
    -storepass "$ANDROID_DEBUG_STORE_PASSWORD" \
    -keypass  "$ANDROID_DEBUG_KEY_PASSWORD" \
    -dname "CN=learnlauncher-debug"
See .env.template at repo root for the required env vars.
